metadata.name: Girl with a Deer
metadata.description:
I wanted to draw something fabulous and mysterious at the same time. I always liked being in the forest, so I most likely drew a girl, a young archer who sits on her friend the Majestic Deer.

I am a young artist from Ukraine, or rather from Kharkov. This is my first drop. I would be very grateful to you for your support of me as a young fantasy author!
